fields.name: You're already in the right place!
fields.value:
The fastest way to reach support is by submitting a ticket through the support channel. Start by verifying your subscription status here: <#1227753026694025246>

We'll have a response for you within 24 hours for pro subscribers, and within 48 hours for basic subscribers.

For general questions or troubleshooting, make a new post in <#1227753022424223764> and we'll all pitch in to make sure it gets answered.
